# VESSELS ######################################################################
Class: Vessel
    EquivalentTo: (PowerDrivenVessel or SailingVessel or VesselConstrainedByHerDraught or VesselEngagedInFishing or VesselNotUnderCommand or VesselRestrictedInHerAbilityToManoeuvre) and (OwnShip or TargetShip)

Class: OwnShip
    SubClassOf: Vessel

Class: TargetShip
    SubClassOf: Vessel

Class: PowerDrivenVessel
    SubClassOf: Vessel
    
Class: SailingVessel
    SubClassOf: Vessel
    
Class: VesselEngagedInFishing
    SubClassOf: Vessel
    
Class: VesselRestrictedInHerAbilityToManoeuvre
    SubClassOf: Vessel
    
Class: VesselConstrainedByHerDraught
    SubClassOf: Vessel
    
Class: VesselNotUnderCommand
    SubClassOf: Vessel
    
DisjointClasses: Vessel, Scenario
DisjointClasses: OwnShip, TargetShip
DisjointClasses: PowerDrivenVessel, SailingVessel, VesselEngagedInFishing, VesselRestrictedInHerAbilityToManoeuvre, VesselConstrainedByHerDraught, VesselNotUnderCommand

